50|$|In Estonia, <b>plea</b> <b>bargaining</b> was {{introduced}} in the 1990s: the penalty is reduced in exchange for confession and avoiding most of the court proceedings. <b>Plea</b> <b>bargaining</b> is permitted for the crimes punishable by no more than four years of imprisonment. Normally, a 25% reduction of the penalty is given.|$|E
